Netflix Original TV Series

‘Altered Carbon’: Season 1

Starts streaming: Feb. 2

Save To Watch Ribbon Save to Watch Like Heart Shape Like

This promising (and expensive-looking) Netflix Original series has a “Blade Runner” look and an intriguing premise, set in a future where human consciousness can be preserved on disks and transferred to new bodies. Joel Kinnaman plays one such body, a handsome specimen with martial-arts skills who’s trying to solve a murder while experiencing echoes of previous corporeal forms. “Altered Carbon” has the look of modern noir — and a reputed abundance of sex and violence to match — but the premise opens up the possibility for a hard sci-fi treatment of memory and identity.

